<li><a href="/wiki/Port_Chicago_disaster" title="Port Chicago disaster">Port Chicago disaster</a> in <a href="/wiki/World_War_II" title="World War II">World War II</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bombay_Explosion_(1944)" title="Bombay Explosion (1944)">Bombay Explosion (1944)</a>, explosion on a ship in Bombay Harbor.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Texas_City_disaster" title="Texas City disaster" class="mw-redirect">Texas City disaster</a>, A <a href="/wiki/Texas" title="Texas">Texas</a> incident also involving a French registered ship carrying explosive cargo</li>
</ul>
