<li><a href="http://novascotia.com/site-ns/media/novascotia/hfxmetro.pdf" class="external text" title="http://novascotia.com/site-ns/media/novascotia/hfxmetro.pdf" rel="nofollow">Halifax Metro Area</a> - Guide</li>
