</ul>
</div>
<p><b>The Halifax Explosion in popular media</b></p>
<ul>
<li><i>The Irish Chain</i> by Barbara Haworth Attard, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0006392156" class="internal">ISBN 0-00-639215-6</a>. (Fictitious novel)</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><i>Burden of Desire</i> by Robert McNeil, 1992 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/015600609X" class="internal">ISBN 0-15-600609-X</a>. (Fictitious novel)</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><i>Thermometers Melting</i> by Glenn Grant, in <i>Arrowdreams: an anthology of alternate Canadas</i>, 1997 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0921833512" class="internal">ISBN 0-921833-51-2</a>. (Fictitious Short Story)</li>
</ul>
